10 亿元人民币（1.4068 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 09:21:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/jdcom-wins-antimonopoly-lawsuit-against-alibaba-2023-12-29/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达为中国推出新游戏芯片以遵守美国出口管制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-launches-new-gaming-chip-china-comply-with-us-export-controls-2023-12-29/</link><description>美国芯片制造商英伟达周四推出了先进游戏芯片的改进版本，旨在遵守美国针对中国的出口管制。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 07:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-launches-new-gaming-chip-china-comply-with-us-export-controls-2023-12-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国的烟花爆竹禁令在农历新年前引发激烈争论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fireworks-ban-sparks-fiery-debate-ahead-lunar-new-year-2023-12-29/</link><description>中国立法者周五在网上就是否应该用烟花爆竹来迎接二月农历新年的激烈争论进行了讨论，称在发明烟花爆竹的中国全面禁止烟花爆竹将很难实施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 07:28:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fireworks-ban-sparks-fiery-debate-ahead-lunar-new-year-2023-12-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>